snippet.textDisplay: My Boyfriend had a sales job that took him to the Philippines for 3 weeks He set up with my work 2 weeks off  I landed in Manila where he was waiting for me  Long surprize story short We were at Starbucks And he had ordered Banoffee pie  Which looked very werid  It came in a Tiffany & Co. box with the lid on the side of the plate Set on top of the whip cream was 3 Charms A airplane, A taxi, And a shoe charm  And a note : Life is a journey Happiness is sharing it   He then pulled out a Tiffany braclet with the Tiffany color on the bands  It was my first time having Banoffee pie  The two baristas that helped him set up the gift were almost in tears He tipped them both $40 Which was almost what they made a week  By then all 3 of us was in tears lol   My man has game : )
